          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": ""
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "  还有 %lld 项，打开应用查看": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "  %lld more — open the app to view"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    " 等": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": " and more"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "（可选，保存到系统钥匙串）": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Optional, saved to the system Keychain)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "（可选，给私钥加密）": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Optional, encrypts the private key)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "（可选）": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Optional)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "（无指纹）": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(No fingerprint)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "（私钥有 passphrase 时填写）": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "(Fill in if the private key has a passphrase)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」在编辑器中有未保存的修改。重新加载会丢弃这些修改。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" has unsaved changes in the editor. Reloading will discard them."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」在远端已不存在，已为你移除并定位到上级目录。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" no longer exists on the remote. It has been removed and you've been taken to the parent directory."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」是一个远程桌面会话，关闭后将断开连接。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" is a Remote Desktop session. Closing it will disconnect."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」有尚未保存的修改，关闭后修改将丢失。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" has unsaved changes. Closing it will discard them."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」有正在运行的进程，关闭后进程将被终止。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" has a running process. Closing it will terminate the process."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」要如何发送到当前终端？": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "How should \"%@\" be sent to the current Terminal?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」要如何打开？": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "How should \"%@\" be opened?"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」远端已存在": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" already exists on the remote"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「%@」需要填入以下变量：": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "\"%@\" requires the following variables:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "「新窗口」打开时，新的远程桌面窗口是否默认进入全屏": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "When opening in a new window, whether new Remote Desktop windows enter full screen by default."
          }
        }
      }
    },
