    "RDP 连接成功后内嵌为标签还是在新窗口打开；「每次询问」会弹出选择且可记住": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Whether a successful RDP connection opens as an embedded tab or in a new window. \"Always Ask\" prompts you to choose and can remember your choice."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "RDP 连接的本地与远端剪贴板双向同步纯文本（复制粘贴互通）；关闭则两端剪贴板互不影响": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sync plain text between the local and remote clipboards in both directions for RDP connections (copy and paste across both). When off, the two clipboards stay independent."
          }
        }
      }
    },
