    "在服务器上开一个监听端口，连进来的流量经隧道送回本机能访问的「目标」（把本地服务暴露给服务器侧）。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Open a listening port on the server; incoming traffic is tunneled to a target reachable from this Mac (exposes a local service to the server side)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "在本机开一个 SOCKS5 代理端口，应用走它即可让流量从服务器出口（无需指定目标）。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Open a SOCKS5 proxy port on this Mac; apps that use it route traffic out through the server (no target needed)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "在本机开一个监听端口，连进来的流量经隧道送到「目标」——目标地址由服务器解析，故 localhost 指服务器自身（访问只监听内网的远程服务）。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Open a listening port on this Mac; incoming traffic is tunneled to a target resolved by the server, so localhost means the server itself (reach a remote service bound only to its private network)."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "在监听端开放的端口，连接它的流量进入隧道。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "The port opened on the listening side; traffic that connects to it enters the tunnel."
          }
        }
      }
    },
