    "该主机为「每次询问」，输入密码连接成功后，将在本次运行内采集监控数据。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This host is set to \"Always Ask.\" After you connect successfully with a password, monitoring data will be collected for this session."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "该主机的证书与上次信任的不一致。若非你主动更换证书，可能存在中间人窃听风险，请谨慎确认。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This host's certificate does not match the one you previously trusted. If you didn't change it yourself, there may be a man-in-the-middle risk. Please confirm carefully."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "该主机的配置（含保存的密码、会话历史、端口转发规则）将被删除，不可恢复。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This host's configuration (including saved passwords, session history, and port forwarding rules) will be deleted permanently."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "该文件在编辑器中有未保存的修改，标签未同步——保存仍会写到原文件名，建议先保存或关闭后再重命名。": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
